Varying different values of lambda: It can be seen that as the values of lambda increase the smoothness of the output increases. For lesser values of lambda, the noise is observed to be extremely high.

In [16]:
lam_list=[1,10,20,50,100,200,500]
In [15]:
for i in lam_list:
    
    unaries = (np.dstack([gray_img, -gray_img]).copy("C")).astype(np.int32)
    pairwise = -1*i * np.eye(2, dtype=np.int32)
    result = cut_simple(unaries, pairwise)
    print("lambda = ",i)
    plt.imshow(result)
    plt.show()
